Third-Party Standards

The BRC drafts in this repository are derived from, and intended for
contribution back to, the published BRC standards maintained by BSV
Blockchain. Magic, protocol-version, and frame-format constants are
inherited from BRC-12 and BRC-124. The full standards catalogue is
maintained at:

  BSV Blockchain Standards Repository
  https://github.com/bitcoin-sv/BRCs/

Specific BRCs referenced by this documentation include BRC-12, BRC-30,
BRC-124, BRC-126, BRC-127, BRC-128, BRC-129, BRC-130, BRC-131, BRC-132,
BRC-133, BRC-134, BRC-135, BRC-136 (tracked upstream only), and
BRC-139.

